name: Corporal Kensaric
Lore: 'Scout responsible for covering the tracks of General Solo''s strike team. Served under Bren Derlin during the Battle of Hoth.',
Text: 'When present at an exterior site battleground site with your other scout, adds 2 (or 1 if Goo Nee Tay on table) to deploy cost of opponent''s characters, vehicles and starships to same site.',
